sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as DSP API Server
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant WFC as workflow-controller<br/>9090/TCP Metrics<br/>6060/TCP Healthz
    participant Pod as Workflow Pod
    participant Exec as argoexec (emissary)
    participant User as User Container
    participant S3 as Artifact Store<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    DSP->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8s-->>WFC: Watch event: new Workflow<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    WFC->>WFC: Reconcile Workflow<br/>(leader-elected singleton)
    WFC->>K8s: Create Pod spec with argoexec<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token

    Note over Pod,User: Pod starts with init + emissary containers

    K8s-->>Pod: Schedule Pod
    Exec->>S3: Load input artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, AccessKey/IAM
    S3-->>Exec: Artifact data
    Exec->>User: Execute wrapped command<br/>(filesystem: /var/run/argo/)
    User-->>Exec: Exit code + stdout/stderr<br/>(signal files on shared emptyDir)
    Exec->>S3: Save output artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, AccessKey/IAM
    Exec->>K8s: Create WorkflowTaskResult CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8s-->>WFC: Watch event: TaskResult<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    WFC->>WFC: Update Workflow status

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 2: Workflow Archival (Optional)

    WFC->>DB: Archive completed Workflow<br/>TCP 5432/3306, SSL configurable
    WFC->>K8s: Update Workflow status<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 3: Artifact Garbage Collection

    WFC->>K8s: Create WorkflowArtifactGCTask CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8s-->>Exec: GC task scheduled
    Exec->>S3: Delete artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, AccessKey/IAM
    Exec->>K8s: Update GCTask status<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
